title: UA ARCHITECH – 3D-PRINTED IN BALTIMORE
description:
To build the perfect foundation for athletes, we looked at perfect structures in nature and architecture. We now have the blueprint for infinite footwear innovation. 

This is the UA ARCHITECH, a performance training shoe that is designed with a custom functional 3D-printed midsole that gives us the key to the future – custom underfoot innovation for every athlete – printed in Baltimore. 

UA ARCHITECT: Build Great Athletes.
